{"tid":2197094,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"擺啲飛機杯喺街咪可以減少流浪狗數目","createTime":"2020-09-10T11:03:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T11:27:49.000Z","uid":51346,"like":60,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"b2b2a3f1d0cda0c9d4cd96b73e3c7049d222a075","tid":2197094,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T11:03:30.000Z","msg":"幫流浪狗打飛機能否有效減少流浪狗的數目？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2070161\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2070161</a><br />\n參考返我之前個post 獸醫絕育貴 義工打飛機又要人手 <br />\n咁如果我哋放啲飛機杯等啲流浪狗diy呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等啲狗丁到虛脫 咪可以減少佢哋做愛嘅次數<br />\n<br />\n首先個飛機杯外型要吸引到流浪狗 眾所周知 啲狗仔最鍾意un人腳 所以個外型設計到成隻人腳咁 而上面個窿就係個飛機杯啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8J1EuTn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8J1EuTn.jpg&h=98cf3a3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後呢個係個窿嘅橫切面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u7xsDN7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu7xsDN7.jpg&h=0af76454&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啲粒粒就係粒粒啦 刺激下條丁 等佢快快手射完到下個<br />\n<br />\n最後你會見到入口左右兩邊油咗紅色嘅 呢個係plan b嚟 改裝自淘寶啲包皮切割器 一切即縫合傷口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由中央系統控制 <br />\n 當然plan b 非必要都唔會用 只有到情況壞到不能再壞 先會考慮...."},{"pid":"7031af3939c26178ecaebff723c8145b076bfcf7","tid":2197094,"uid":350634,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T11:10:28.000Z","msg":"淨係適合你呢隻厹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6bea059cb4eaa76f21c898af03381cdd5824877","tid":2197094,"uid":249885,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T11:10:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4aa86c3d5f5103960dd4ffa9f3d63bd4f363269","tid":2197094,"uid":165232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T11:15:09.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"80c564092648a4eed265f4fea063d7c680090b96","tid":2197094,"uid":286155,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,